release.notes:
Comes with a printed inner sleeve containing track list, credits and other additional information. Sunburst labels with asterisk next to side number. Track B6 is an untitled locked groove with a short message from a child's voice.

Recorded in Los Angeles at Musicland West, Sunset Sound, Oasis, Soundfactory & Georgios Spaceschiff.

℗ 1983 CBS Inc. / © 1983 CBS Inc.
Made in Holland / Distribué en France par CBS Disques.

Runouts:
"MASTERED AT ALLEN ZENTZ L.A., CALIF." is stamped, everything else is etched.
